title: Oakley Batwolf Polarized Sunglasses OO910104 Overview
description:
Oakley Batwolf Matte Black and Grey Polarized Lens Mens Sunglasses  - OO910104- http://www.abt.com/product/71938/Oakley-OO910104.html

Features:
• Frame:
o Interchangeable Square O Icons
o Comfortable fit on medium to large faces via extended wrapped frame geometry
o Precision and durability of sculpturally integrated hinge mechanisms with dual action CAM
o Durability and all-day comfort of lightweight stress-resistant O Matter frame material
• Lens:
o Oakley HDPolarized –Minimized glare via technology that produces the best polarized lenses on the planet with greater than 99 polarized efficiency
o Optical precision and performance that meets ANSI Z87.1 standards
o Impact resistance that meets ANSI Z87.1 standards for high-mass and high-velocity impact
o UV protection of plutonite lens material that filters out 100 of UVA/ UVB/ UVC& harmful blue light up to 400nm
o Glare reduction and tuned light transmission of Iridium lens coating (optional)
o Grey Polarized
Medium to bright light. Excellent all-purpose lens that cuts blinding glare while offering truer color perception.
 Light Transmission: 17
 Protection Index: 3
 Neutral / Contrast: Neutral
• Accessories:
o Additional pair of interchangeable Square O icons included
